lead_paragraph: Diamond DeShields scored 21 points, Bashaara Graves added 19 and Tennessee beat No. 15 Texas A&M 70-60 in the Southeastern Conference tournament Friday.

headline.print_headline: Tennessee Women Beat No. 15 A&M 70-60 for 3rd Straight Win
